                        <p part="N">卷軸</p>
                        <decoNote>
                                    The handscroll with narrow borders (小鑲手卷) features a protective and decorative backing (錦包首) crafted from light brown silk adorned with elegant blue and brown patterns. The title label is meticulously made of yellow Chinese paper. The 'Heaven' section (天) is elegantly fashioned from pale-blue silk, exhibiting signs of damage. Vertical stripes (隔水) are composed of jacquard beige silk. The frontispiece (引首) is expertly crafted from traditional yellow Chinese paper, while the colophon section (拖尾) is made from traditional Chinese white paper.
                                    小鑲手卷，天為淺藍色絲織物，有磨損痕跡。隔水為米白色有花紋絲織物。引首為黃色紙本，拖尾為白色紙本，略有污跡。邊為淺棕色絲織物。錦包首為棕色絲織物伴有淺棕色花紋，八寶帶為紫色絲織物和別子為玉制，題簽為黃色紙本。
